<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.7.4">
<l>kūṭā viraṇiyaṉaik kūrukirāl mārviṭanta</l>
<l>vōṭā vaṭalariyai yumparār kōmaṉai</l>
<l>tōṭār naṟuntuḻāy mārvaṉai yārvattāl</l>
<l>pāṭātār pāṭṭeṉṟum pāṭṭalla kēṭṭāmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The songs of those who do not sing with passion of the celestials’ king,</l>
<l>The unretreating battle lion which, with sharp claws,</l>
<l rend="indent">pierced the chest of lifeless Hiraṇya,</l>
<l>The one on whose chest is blossom-covered scented tulasī,</l>
<l>Are never songs; [this] we have heard.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
